body:
Heaven Will Be Mine is a visual novel by Aevee Bee and Max Schwartz. The story is set in an alternate history post-Cold War universe wherein humanity has split into three warring factions, known as the Memorial Foundation, Cradle's Graces, and the Celestial Mechanics. Over the course of the game the player, through interactions with the other two faction pilots, can gradually push one of these three factions toward dominance over space and humanity's future. 

It is a sequel to [[We Know the Devil]]. 

h4. Main Characters:
* {{luna-terra_(heaven_will_be_mine)|Luna-Terra}}, pilot of the {{mare_crisium_(heaven_will_be_mine)|Mare Crisium}}
* {{pluto_(heaven_will_be_mine)|Pluto}}, pilot of the {{krun_macula_(heaven_will_be_mine)|Krun Macula}}
* {{saturn_(heaven_will_be_mine)|Saturn}}, pilot of the {{string_of_pearls_(heaven_will_be_mine)|String of Pearls}}

We Know the Devil is a visual novel by Aevee Bee and Max Schwartz. The plot centers on three girls at a Christian summer camp, sent alone to a cabin to confront the devil. Its sequel is [[Heaven Will Be Mine]]. 

h4. Main Characters
* {{jupiter_(we_know_the_devil)|Jupiter}}
* {{neptune_(we_know_the_devil)|Neptune}}
